Super Minimal Blog Split License
===============================

This repository contains two categories of material:

1. Reusable Materials
	- build.py
	- static/style.css
    - templates/

2. Content
	- posts/
    - static/, except style.css
	- any generated output derived from files in posts/
	  (including corresponding HTML pages, feed entries, and excerpts)

